overview: If you’re going to get anywhere in the business world, sometimes it’s more than just working hard. And in GENTLEMEN 31, what it’s truly all about is EXECUTIVE SUBMISSION! Sergeant Miles pumps Beaux Banks’ hole deep and raw. Isaac X and Adam Gray negotiate a business deal via flip-fucking. Alpha Wolfe makes Alfonso Osnaya work hard for his promotion. And both Issac X and Beaux Banks both return for after-hours sodomy!
title: Gentlemen 31: Executive Submission
